headline: Hologic (HOLX) Tops Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Hologic (HOLX) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 0.98% and 0.34%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
